text: Accidents Will Happen is a 1938 American drama movie directed by William Clemens and starring Ronald Reagan, Gloria Blondell, Dick Purcell, Sheila Bromley, Addison Richards, Hugh O'Connell, Elliott Sullivan, Anderson Lawler. It was distributed by Warner Bros.. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1938 drama movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by William Clemens
